tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select DISTINCT useraction.apdexCategory, count(*) FROM usersession where useraction.apdexCategory <> "UNKNOWN" GROUP BY useraction.apdexCategory

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT DISTINCT count(userSessionId) as "Sessões" FROM usersession WHERE useraction.apdexCategory = "SATISFIED"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT DISTINCT DATETIME(starttime, 'MM-dd', '1d'), count(*) as "Sessões Satisfeitas" FROM usersession WHERE useraction.apdexCategory = "SATISFIED"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select DISTINCT DATETIME(starttime, 'MM-dd', '1d'), count(*) as "Sessões que contém erro" FROM usersession where useraction.errorCount = 0

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT DISTINCT count(userSessionId) as "Sessões" FROM usersession WHERE useraction.apdexCategory = "TOLERATING"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT DISTINCT count(userSessionId) as "Sessões" FROM usersession WHERE useraction.apdexCategory = "FRUSTRATED"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT DISTINCT DATETIME(starttime, 'MM-dd', '1d'), count(*) as "Sessões Satisfeitas" FROM usersession WHERE useraction.apdexCategory = "TOLERATING"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT DISTINCT DATETIME(starttime, 'MM-dd', '1d'), count(*) as "Sessões Frustradas" FROM usersession WHERE useraction.apdexCategory = "FRUSTRATED"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select isp, count(*) from usersession where isp is not null group by isp

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select top(city ,5) as 'Municípios', count(*) as '# Sessões' from usersession where city is not null GROUP BY city

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select top(region ,5) as 'Estados', count(*) as '# Sessões' from usersession where region is not null GROUP BY region

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select top(browserType, 6) as 'Top Browsers', count(*) as '# Sessões'  from usersession where browserType is not null GROUP BY browserType

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select top(browserMajorVersion, 6) as 'Top Browsers', count(*) as '# Sessões'  from usersession where browserMajorVersion is not null GROUP BY browserMajorVersion

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.customName: Funil de Satisfação  -  Atual vs 1 semana atrás
tiles.query: SELECT FUNNEL (useraction.apdexCategory ="SATISFIED" as "Satisfeitos", useraction.apdexCategory= "TOLERATING" as "Tolerantes", useraction.apdexCategory= "FRUSTRATED" as "Frustrados") FROM usersession
